  "title": "Event crew member!!!!",
  "description": "<p>🌟Events Crew Member!!! - Join the team now!🌟<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for reliable, energetic, and hardworking individuals to join our team as Events Crew Members. In this role, you will help set up, operate, and pack down events while supporting the event team to ensure everything runs smoothly. This position is ideal for people who enjoy hands-on work and fast-paced environments.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Help maintain a clean, safe, and organized event space</li><li>Follow directions from supervisors and work well with the team</li><li>Provide general on-site support during the event as needed</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Positive attitude and strong teamwork skills</li><li>Able to follow instructions and work in a busy environment</li><li>Comfortable lifting light to moderate equipment</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and able to work flexible hours</li><li>Good communication and customer service skills</li></ul>",
